| למד | learned |
| אכל | ate |
| שׁתה | drank |

## Grammar

- Past tense qal verbs (perfect form)
- Basic subject-verb agreement (3rd person masculine singular and plural)
- Definite article (ה) with nouns
- Prepositions with nouns
- Basic word order (VSO and SVO patterns)
- Construct relationships (simple)
- Direct object marker (את)
- Conjunction (ו) for connecting verbs and clauses
- Basic adjectival agreement
- Simple pronominal suffixes on nouns
